ytic expression that assumes noise\nproperties are uniquely described by their power spectrum. Along with our\npublic code, $\\mathtt{mnms}$, this work establishes a necessary element in the\nscience pipelines of both ACT DR6 and future ground-based CMB experiments such\nas the Simons Observatory (SO).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Mar 2023 19:04:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-09"}
