address omitted variable bias. Using\ntransaction-level export data from Bangladesh, I find that 10% higher\nper-shipment costs reduce the shipping frequency by 3.45%. The findings are\nrobust to different specifications and subsamples.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Mar 2023 20:32:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-09"}
