reum, bots in\nfixed gas price blockchains are not battling a gas war; they are fighting in a\nlatency war.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Mar 2023 21:28:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-09"}
