ic spintronics on a firm basis\nand paving the way for studying exotic quantum phenomena in related materials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Mar 2023 13:03:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 26 Mar 2023 01:57:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-28"}
