 contribution of faint versus bright galaxies\ndepends on redshift, with UV bright galaxies ($-23 <$ $M_{UV}$ $< -19$)\nbecoming more important over time and reaching $\\approx 40\\%$ at the end of\nreionization around $z=6$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Mar 2023 13:37:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 9 Mar 2023 03:39:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-10"}
